---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "PRP Microneedling | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Collagen induction therapy enhanced with your own growth factors.", "canonical": "/services/prp-microneedling", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-white text-neutral-900 pt-28 md:pt-32">
  <!-- HERO Light -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-neutral-700">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/services" class="hover:text-neutral-700">Services</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span class="text-neutral-800">PRP Microneedling</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="py-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">PRP Microneedling</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl">Collagen induction therapy enhanced with your own growth factors.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Consultation‑first</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Personalized plan</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Clear aftercare</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="h-px w-full bg-neutral-200"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <!-- Main narrative -->
    <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-10">
      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">What it treats</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">We focus on concerns commonly addressed by this service and tailor the plan to your goals and anatomy.</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Targets and areas vary by indication</li>
          <li>Balanced, proportionate outcomes</li>
          <li>Comfort‑forward approach</li>
          <li>Clear, realistic expectations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Ideal candidates</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Healthy individuals with specific concerns and realistic expectations. Certain conditions, medications, or allergies may require modifications or make a service unsuitable.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Educational only—not medical advice. Review your history with your provider.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">How it works</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Step 1</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Consult & planning</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Goal setting, mapping, and tailored plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Step 2</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Treatment</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Technique matched to indication and area.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Step 3</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Aftercare</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Clear guidance and next steps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Results & longevity</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Onset</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Varies by service</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Peak</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Discussed at consult</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Duration</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Maintenance as advised</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Safety & aftercare</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Follow your personalized post‑care handout</li>
          <li>Protect the area and avoid irritants as directed</li>
          <li>Hydration, rest, and recommended products only</li>
          <li>Report unexpected reactions promptly</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">FAQs</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-neutral-700">
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">How many sessions will I need?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">It varies by concern and modality. Your provider will outline a personalized plan and maintenance if appropriate.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Will it look natural?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Our approach focuses on subtle, harmonious changes that complement your features.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Is there downtime?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Most services have minimal downtime. Temporary redness, swelling, or sensitivity can occur and usually resolves quickly.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- Side panel -->
    <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900">Key Facts</h4>
        <dl class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-neutral-700">
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Session length</dt><dd>~30–60 minutes</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Downtime</dt><dd>Minimal</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Discomfort</dt><dd>Mild to moderate</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Maintenance</dt><dd>Personalized</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900">Good to know</h4>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">We’ll review your goals, medical history, and preferences to create a plan that fits your lifestyle and budget.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
